text: Cynisca ivoirensis is a worm lizard species in the family Amphisbaenidae. It is endemic to Ivory Coast. ==References== Category:Cynisca (lizard) Category:Reptiles described in 2014 Category:Taxa named by Jean-François Trape Category:Taxa named by Youssouph Mané Category:Endemic fauna of Ivory Coast
title: Cynisca ivoirensis
